       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. HELLO-WORLD.
       AUTHOR. COBOL FLOW HUB.
       DATE-WRITTEN. 2025-01-26.
      *
      * SIMPLE HELLO WORLD PROGRAM FOR TESTING
      *
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-MESSAGE            PIC X(50) VALUE 'HELLO FROM COBOL!'.
       01  WS-COUNTER            PIC 9(3) VALUE 0.
       
       COPY TEST-CONSTANTS.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-PROCESS.
           PERFORM DISPLAY-MESSAGE
           PERFORM COUNT-LOOP
           CALL 'UTILITY-PROGRAM' USING WS-MESSAGE
           STOP RUN.

       DISPLAY-MESSAGE.
           DISPLAY WS-MESSAGE.

       COUNT-LOOP.
           PERFORM VARYING WS-COUNTER FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL WS-COUNTER > 5
               DISPLAY 'COUNT: ' WS-COUNTER
           END-PERFORM. 